Package kbp2013.wikipedia

Various tools related to usage of Wikipedia XML dumps.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnnotateWithKB
    This class finds a KB key from KBP according to a surface form.
    GetRewritingFromWikipedia
    This class makes use of Lucene-search v2.1 for wiki (in use with Wikimedia wiki's) "do You Mean" functionality to correct a misspelled query.
